headline: Humana price target raised to $315 from $290 at Wells Fargo
summary: Wells Fargo analyst Stephen Baxter raised the firm’s price target on Humana (HUM) to $315 from $290 and keeps an Overweight rating on the shares as the firm updates Managed Care estimates post-election. All estimates assume the expiration of enhanced exchange subsidies for 2026, Wells notes. The firm believes Medicare Advantage risk/reward improves with Republicans, although areas of concern still exist.
